Besalco to Invest $626 Million in Chile and Peru, Segunda Says

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-04-07T18:36:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/besalco-to-invest-626-million-in-chile-and-peru-segunda-says.html
Besalco SA (BESALCO) , a Chilean construction
company, plans to invest $626 million within the next three
years in Chile and  Peru , mostly in civil works, equipment
purchases, land acquisitions for real estate projects and power
generation projects, La Segunda said, citing Besalco chairman
Victor Bezanilla.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson in Santiago at 
 ethomson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  